# CoDIRA version in navbar

The app version is shown in the top navbar in **ERSimulatorApp/Pages/Shared/_Layout.cshtml** as `CoDIRA vX.Y.Z`.

- **With each code change** you make to the project, **increment the 3rd number (patch)** in that string, e.g. `v1.1.1` → `v1.1.2`, then `v1.1.3`.
- **Do not** increment the 1st (major) or 2nd (minor) number unless the user explicitly asks to (e.g. "bump minor version" or "release 2.0.0").

Apply the version bump in the same edit that makes the change, so the navbar always reflects the latest update.
